--- !u!1001 &155707002
PrefabInstance:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  serializedVersion: 2
  m_Modification:
    m_TransformParent: {fileID: 407672899}
    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 4657501828349135716, guid: 652433bafe41c1c4ca81c1db8e43f4fb, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Are you nervous? Well, you shouldn''t be. It''s just a bunch of meat
        sacks after all. They don''t even have guns!



        Now to the important
        parts:

        - To move your hoard, just click on the position you want
        them to move with the left mouse button.

        - To move the camera, use
        the WSAD-Keys or bring your cursor near the screen border.



        Easy
        enough, isn''t it?



        It is essential that you kill as many survivors
        as you can. Some will fight and some will run away. Just kill everything
        nearby and make sure you lose as few zombies as you can.



        Have
        fun killing!'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4657501828349135716, guid: 652433bafe41c1c4ca81c1db8e43f4fb, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_fontSize
